  "3337180": {
    "name": " 小小的岛",
    "steam_appid": 3337180,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337180/extras/9ff74322b7eb289a7df7b3e33ad1f219.avif?t=1770104524\" width=680 height=71 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《小小的岛》是一款轻松治愈的模拟经营建造游戏，在这里你将邂逅一个神秘的精灵文明，并帮助这些小生灵在一座与世隔绝的岛屿上重建家园。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里，你可以种植可爱的魔法作物，收集充满能量的水晶；钓起并收集奇幻的小鱼；吸引迷人的动物居民与精灵前来定居。利用收集到的水晶扩展岛屿的版图，解锁越来越丰富的可爱植物种类，包括魔法蘑菇、多肉植物和各色花卉。你可以自由塑造岛屿的模样，按照自己的审美喜好，让这片被遗忘的土地在悠闲的节奏中重新焕发生机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏既提供持续交互、值得反复操作的游玩空间，也支持完整的放置玩法，让你既能深度参与系统搭配，又能在忙碌时轻松挂机推进进度，度过一段轻松惬意的闲暇时光。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你正在寻找一款既有丰富玩法、又能让心情慢慢沉静下来的治愈游戏，《小小的岛》或许会成为你的那座小小港湾。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337180/extras/b1879a185183bb420897e7cdb5c72810.avif?t=1770104524\" width=680 height=68 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 上手简单易学，没有复杂的数值系统或让人头大的经营管理。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💎 在岛屿各处种植作物，收获水晶，并用它们解锁全新的植物品种，逐步扩展你的领地！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌱 每种作物都拥有自己的“超能力”！有的负责生产，有的负责运输，还有的能提升收益——合理搭配，让你的水晶产量飞速增长！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337180/extras/2ad38b3c30515b212cb4e05b6ebe3892.avif?t=1770104524\" width=1360 height=809 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337180/extras/50303cbb7bff2fa9566e07344890d21a.avif?t=1770104524\" width=1360 height=809 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337180/extras/b70fc70721de7399a738fbb618f87c89.avif?t=1770104524\" width=680 height=82 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌳 除了岛屿原有的居民外，你还可以通过树洞招募新的居民，让他们暂时在岛上停留生活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧚‍♀️ 每位居民都拥有独特的外观与性格，并会以各自不同的方式协助岛屿的生产与发展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏘️ 与居民们建立深厚的友谊，他们就会在你的岛屿上永久定居，把这里当作真正的家！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337180/extras/202bfe4f0af8d04a8c7c0eccee23fd2d.avif?t=1770104524\" width=1360 height=936 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337180/extras/11442186a51d69aedb3b9a2133c997a7.avif?t=1770104524\" width=1360 height=809 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337180/extras/434f9c7881d6783d4ef63f0be9d2da4e.avif?t=1770104524\" width=680 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎣 在岛屿各处抛出鱼线，享受一段轻松惬意的钓鱼时光！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐟 钓起各种各样的鱼类，随着技巧不断提升，挑战更大的体型纪录，甚至向传说中的「鱼王」发起挑战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337180/extras/f9d15618339371ce5fe11fc73d6b8ea6.avif?t=1770104524\" width=1360 height=809 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337180/extras/d7c8cca3bdaba4c8af5e9c9e9c94bb22.avif?t=1770104524\" width=1360 height=809 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337180/extras/9d91156f53482d9ac711920ab2edc8a8.avif?t=1770104524\" width=680 height=76 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >☀️ 你的岛屿会随着时间流逝与天气变化展现不同氛围——阳光明媚的景色、飘雪静谧的雪天、气势十足的风暴，还有水母点亮夜空的夜晚，以及划过天际的流星之夜，处处藏着充满魔法感的惊喜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337180/extras/88f3ae08038ebcdd4ad023961bef2081.avif?t=1770104524\" width=1360 height=809 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337180/extras/931aac560e10215e34da82e73881df7a.avif?t=1770104524\" width=1360 height=809 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337180/extras/a8aaa81edebf87be0b281593a888b72c.avif?t=1770104524\" width=1360 height=809 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337180/extras/e2f6f66336926e24ffc46d0bcb940ade.avif?t=1770104524\" width=680 height=76 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感谢大家对《小小的岛》的关注与支持！如果你在游戏中遇到任何问题，或是有新奇的想法与创意，都欢迎加入我们的官方 Q 群（980120059），让我们一起让这座小岛变得更加美好！</p>",
